  for example. This JSON can be used by mobile apps which don't require a backend service or even a sqlite database.

%p.apps_text
  It's like
  %a{href: "https://parse.com/", target: "_blank"}
    Parse
  for read-only data. 
  JSON APIs can be used from Ruby, Python, Javascript, iOS and Android apps without any special SDK. See usage examples
  %a{href: "/tutorial/use", target: "_blank"}
    here   

%br

%p.apps_text
